name: Houston I Think We Angered The Eldritch Gods
name_original: Houston I Think We Angered The Eldritch Gods
description:
Houston I Think We Angered The Eldritch Gods - by Orange Elephant

Controls:

-W/A/S/D - Move around

- Space - Shoot

Guidelines:

-  Kill all the enemies in order to win.

- There are fuel planets to fill your fuel by 20%.

- If an enemy touch you, you lose.

- If your fuel runs out, you lose.
